description: Sometimes the best food is the messiest, so roll up your sleeves, Orlando! The Garbage Can is slopping out some of the best messy food there is. Go hog wild with The Pig Pen - saucy Hog Wings with Salt Potatoes and Bacon Bleu Mac & Cheese. Get pumped for The Dumpster - A heaping pile of Macaroni Salad, French Fries, Cheeseburger, Meat Sauce, and Diced Onions. The Trash Bag makes for the perfect take out - Doritos or Fritos with Meat Sauce and Shredded Cheddar. We’re talkin’ some seriously tasty trash. Come out to The Garbage Can and delight in this delicious dump!
name: The Garbage Can
